Error 1- Unable to write file '/home/welcome1/shell_scripting/hello.sh' (NoPermissions (FileSystemError): Error: EACCES: permission denied, open '/home/welcome1/shell_scripting/hello.sh')

Solution- Need to change the file permission

sudo chown -R username path or sudo chown -R path 

Error 2- 'Username' is not in the sudoers file. 

Solution - 

Open file
su root 
nano /etc/sudoers

Then add the user below admin user like below syntax.
user_name ALL=(ALL)  ALL

